#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Sharing files with OnionShare\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Compartilhando arquivos com OnionShare\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"[OnionShare](https://onionshare.org/) is a tool to share files of any size "
"securely and anonymously."
msgstr ""
"[OnionShare](https://onionshare.org/) é uma ferramenta para compartilhar "
"arquivos de qualquer tamanho de forma segura e anônima."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span> creates an onion address\n"
"that someone else can visit in <span class=\"application\">Tor\n"
"Browser</span> to access the files that you want to share.\n"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span> cria um endereço onion\n"
"que outra pessoa pode visitar usando o <span class=\"application\">"
"Navegador\n"
"Tor</span> para acessar os arquivos que você quer compartilhar.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "To share files with <span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span>:\n"
msgstr ""
"Para compartilhar arquivos com <span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span>:"
"\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Open the <span class=\"application\">Files</span> browser."
msgstr "Abra o navegador de <span class=\"application\">Arquivos</span>."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Right-click (on Mac, click with two fingers) on the files or folders that "
"you want to share and choose <span class=\"guilabel\">Share via OnionShare</"
"span>.  <span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span> starts."
msgstr ""
"Clique com o botão direito (no Mac, clique com dois dedos) nos arquivos ou "
"pastas que você quer compartilhar e escolha <span class=\"guilabel\">"
"Compartilhar via OnionShare</span>.  O <span class=\"application\""
">OnionShare</span> inicia."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "To share more files or folders, you can either:"
msgstr ""
"Para compartilhar mais arquivos ou pastas, você pode fazer um dos seguintes:"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid ""
"Drag and drop them from the <span class=\"application\">Files</span> browser "
"onto <span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span>."
msgstr ""
"Arraste-os do navegador de <span class=\"application\">Arquivos</span> para "
"o <span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span>."

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid ""
"Click the <span class=\"guilabel\">Add</span> button in <span class="
"\"application\">OnionShare</span>."
msgstr ""
"Clique no botão <span class=\"guilabel\">Adicionar</span> no <span class=\""
"application\">OnionShare</span>."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Click <span class=\"guilabel\">Start Sharing</span>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   <div class=\"bug\">\n"
"   <p>Starting to share the files can take up to several minutes.</p>\n"
"   </div>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   When the files are available for sharing, an onion address appears at\n"
"   the bottom of <span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   [[!img onionshare.png link=\"no\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "   [[!img onionshare.png link=\"no\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Send this onion address to someone else, for example, by email."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   The other person can download the files by visiting the onion address\n"
"   in <span class=\"application\">Tor Browser</span>.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"<span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span> informs you when the files are "
"being accessed."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   The files are not shared anymore as soon as you close\n"
"   <span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span> or shut down Tails.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   <div class=\"tip\">\n"
"   <p>By default, the files can only be downloaded once. To allow more\n"
"   than one download:</p>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   <ol>\n"
"   <li>Click the [[!img lib/emblem-system.png link=\"no\" class=\"symbolic\"\n"
"   alt=\"Show site information\"]] button to open the settings of\n"
"   <span class=\"application\">OnionShare</span>.</li>\n"
"   <li>Deselect the <span class=\"guilabel\">Stop sharing after first\n"
"   download</span>.</li>\n"
"   <li>Click <span class=\"button\">Save</span>.</li>\n"
"   </ol>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   </div>\n"
msgstr "   </div>\n"
